## RAG Document Chatbot
A retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) chatbot that answers questions over any PDF document.

## Tech stack
- LangChain — RAG pipeline orchestration
- Hugging Face (Llama 3.1 + all-MiniLM-L6-v2) — LLM and embeddings
- Pinecone — vector database for semantic search
- Streamlit — chat interface

## How it works
1. PDF is chunked into 500-token segments
2. Chunks are embedded using sentence-transformers
3. Embeddings stored in Pinecone vector database
4. User query retrieved against top 3 relevant chunks
5. Context + query sent to Llama 3.1 to generate grounded answer
